{
  "stem": "18778.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 497.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'd rather not say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He lives in Brazil.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he didn't see fit to communicate with me whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I-- I do see one of his sisters every year when I go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She lives in Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we commiserate about old times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As I said, her father was my father's partner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so it's-- it's a touch of home for both of us when we get together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There's another friend who lives in Atlanta.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Her name is Erica Hecht.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And her father-- her father or her uncle was the controller in my grandfather's factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were-- we were in the same school, but she's not of the same age.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But there also is a touch of home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, even though we were thrown out-- we were thrown out of our homes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We were kicked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But there is this-- there is this feeling for home and roots that doesn't leave you no matter what.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And some people can't understand that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They can't understand why we would want to go back to Germany, why we would want to be the guests of the nation that didn't want us in the first place.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They don't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "First of all, because we wanted to see each other again, see who's coming.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And secondly, because that's where our roots are.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "One those cemeteries are buried our grandparents and our great-grandparents.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And our communities were built up by some of our contributions and our family's contributions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And most of all, we have the chance to talk to the young people there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was one of my big reasons for going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "When the invitation arrived, first of all, we got a letter from a family who said they were going to be our hosts.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
